# EMX Sports Website - Cursor Rules

## Project
Boxing promotion website for EMX Sports (emxsports.com)
Stack: Next.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS

## Brand
- Primary: #c41e3a (red)
- Gold: #d4a017
- Dark: #0a0a0a
- Font headings: Oswald
- Font body: Inter

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Functional components only, no class components
- Tailwind for all styling, no CSS modules
- shadcn/ui patterns where applicable
- File naming: PascalCase for components, kebab-case for pages/utils

## Fighters
Active roster: Jevgenijs Aleksejevs (20-0-0), Milans Volkovs (12-4-2), Karen Chukhadzhian

## Workflow
- All changes through feature branches
- Test on GitHub Pages before production deploy
- Run `npm run build` before committing
- Keep components small and focused
